== Weirdness ==

=== Setting variables in a FOR loop ===

The code below does NOT work!
 FOR %%A IN (c:\test\*) do (
   set value=something
   echo %value%
 )

This works!
 SETLOCAL ENABLEDELAYEDEXPANSION
 FOR %%A IN (c:\test\*) do (
   set value=something
   echo !value!
 )

